{"tid":324308,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"我想upgrade一下部電腦","createTime":"2017-07-16T10:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T10:58:47.000Z","uid":74846,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c620aadf292e15463f35d99966782de8e08757e6","tid":324308,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"請大家聽下我既目標先：<br />\n<br />\n  目標換I9/R9 連底板，RAM唔知好唔好加多少少，目前用緊16G DDR4，Display card已經決定左升做1080ti，你地會唔會有其他建議?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n  希望做直播時唔會有太大既FPS Drop，E.G.我依加玩Automata時開直播有時會由60跌到得返4X，體驗非常之唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。有上網睇過關於capture card既存在，但係教學同點運作既文都無乜，唔知點樣決定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  P.S我直播都係同FD吹住水打咁既水平，唔係對外開台，但都希望有一定水平既質素出到黎<br />\n<br />\n  另外我都想換一下散熱，唔知巴絲們有咩360既AIO/自組LOOP教學及機箱推薦一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?唔需要太靜，效能優先。機箱我諗都會出返則透既，但冷排真係無從入手。<br />\n<br />\n  關於CPU選擇，性能上I9我諗真係無得輸，但唔太清楚佢熱到點既程度，而R9又未面世，左右兩難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n  關於底板，我諗都係會選擇返ATX SIZE，牌子目前想揀ASUS/GIGA兩個牌子，前者高階板公認勁就唔多講，而GIGA就自己用緊就作為其中一個決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n  關於機箱，我自己無乜去深入了解過機箱，依加用緊既呢個都係事事但但咁落場睇岩就買，唔知各位巴絲有咩心水推薦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n  最後附上用緊既spec<br />\n<br />\nCPU：7700K (受害者之一)<br />\n<br />\n底板：GIGABYTE Z270X GAMING 5 ATX<br />\n<br />\nGPU：GIGABYTE GTX1080 Extreme<br />\n<br />\nRAM：GSKILL TDZ RGB C14 3200 8Gx2<br />\n<br />\nCPUAIO：Corsair H100i v2 (240mm)<br />\n<br />\nCase：CM690 III<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99d87710de3890e4e50ae3a37e6c388263aee72","tid":324308,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"